## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives on overcoming discrimination. The lack of recent data and peer-reviewed studies in the search results limits the depth of analysis. Additionally, the effectiveness of suggested actions may vary based on cultural, social, and individual contexts, which are not fully explored in this report. Further research and empirical studies are recommended to validate and expand upon these findings.